==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: declassify
<hw>declassify</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <def>to lift the restriction on
publication [of documents] by reducing or eliminating the secrecy
classification of; -- usually applied to government documents classified
as secret.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> make available again.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

